   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"20th year of Antoninus Caesar the lord, Phaophi 20. For me Nemesas going to Sko for the collection of the bath-tax there, salary for one month: twenty-four drachmas. Total: 24 drachmas. (2nd hd.) Give the 24 drachmas."</ab>
         </div>
